Is There a Way To Make CSS3 Media Queries Cross-Browser?

Is there anyway to make media queries in CSS3 work cross-browser?
I am having a bit of trouble testing some pages on IE7, and I know that there are certain problems with a media rule like:
@media print{
body{
    color:#000;
}
}

